{"tid":1567952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打死藍絲 你就贏？清醒啊大家","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T19:07:26.000Z","uid":124630,"like":12,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"73522b5fb4e8c17449aceddf2a4956825966edbe","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"呢幾日係好多藍絲出嚟唱歌拆文宣，但佢地做嘅嘢有幾多效果？除咗畀自己友打飛機外影響咗個運動乜嘢？自己友會因為佢地呢啲行為去支持番對家咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果冇，每一次手足們去對抗有咩意思？今日終於打起上嚟，打嗰陣好開心，一下一下車落去，但之後呢？你打死咗佢咁之後呢？手足會被拉被告，狗隻繼續無法無天，支那同林鄭輿論機器全開，五大訴求仲想爭取？<br />\n<br />\n當初大家得到咁多民氣，狗隻721同831助攻唔少，令大家有黃藍是政見，黑白是良知。但到今日，大家去攻擊同自己意見唔同嘅人，同班狗攻擊鬧自己嘅人有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n我同意大家被打要還手，但喺被打之前，我想大家諗下你去藍絲活動場地意義係咩？佢地唱歌撕嘢同我地唱歌貼文宣都係佢地自由，大家忘記咗不守牆，撕一貼十咩？咁點解仲要去現場踩場？當大家叫人唔好去撐警大會免得被打，又會去藍絲場地？本質上有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n天琦講過，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？希望大家諗清楚，唔好被仇恨蒙蔽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8197060e2c5d33e0855b7d5743b8fc7b93f994e9","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2559d592ff9b24cac79d0bd41d42ec27e082473c","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:53:03.000Z","msg":"唔係叫大家唔做啊<br />\n但今日中學生有集會，天水圍有行街，冇人去？"},{"pid":"4f8861de1446fdadeb1f4c73c6fc8ca235307cd8","tid":1567952,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49f42125bb1e21638fcb4b952ea71cf4272d1f01","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"行動post推得好辛苦<br />\n大家如果同意狗同政權先係目標，咁應反思一下今日嘅行動帶嚟乜嘢"},{"pid":"ee05fc5c0ad16afb2027c781d39c5106dbc0f2cd","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"打死藍絲支那唔會有傷害<br />\n佢地只係一個condom<br />\n一個condom換十幾個手足啊"},{"pid":"db8a6650152fdac03fb87da004b7d51e052239e0","tid":1567952,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n[藍警合作模式]  目前對九龍灣嘅觀察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8944b8349080cbab7c0793bee87446b6a42094f","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8nTreP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8nTreP.jpg&h=6c18ef25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8942ca2479518f7d1dcc37ae02166505486069d","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfbf954e215372c53539e97dea9e5c19611c074","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:56:31.000Z","msg":"愛丁堡好少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121273fbc6c3eb1b7d69b58198815bc89280b00e","tid":1567952,"uid":278391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"有人話到每日打爆幾多個藍絲可以有獨立調查同釋放所有義士？"},{"pid":"e1b9dd696e6437c1af9099d58b13445432eab3cb","tid":1567952,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"對藍絲既行動應以<br />\n滲透分化煽動醜化 以主"},{"pid":"9d4897410bbee88107f6851f3ac457c43a70d965","tid":1567952,"uid":124630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:5